### 1) List active vouchers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/active
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### 2) Validate voucher for selected cart items
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vouchers/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "cartItemIds": ["{{CART_ITEM_ID_1}}", "{{CART_ITEM_ID_2}}"]
}

### 3) Admin list vouchers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/vouchers?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### 4) Admin create voucher
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/vouchers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "description": "Giam 10% toi da 20k",
  "type": "PERCENTAGE",
  "value": 10,
  "maxDiscount": 20000,
  "minOrderAmount": 100000,
  "maxUsage": 100,
  "userUsageLimit": 1,
  "startAt": "2026-04-07T02:00:00.000Z",
  "endAt": "2026-04-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "isActive": true,
  "bannerImageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/sample.jpg"
}

### 5) Admin update voucher
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/vouchers/{{VOUCHER_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "description": "Giam 10% toi da 30k",
  "type": "PERCENTAGE",
  "value": 10,
  "maxDiscount": 30000,
  "minOrderAmount": 100000,
  "maxUsage": 200,
  "userUsageLimit": 2,
  "startAt": "2026-04-07T02:00:00.000Z",
  "endAt": "2026-05-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "isActive": true,
  "bannerImageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/sample.jpg"
}

### 6) Admin disable voucher
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/admin/vouchers/{{VOUCHER_ID}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
  "isActive": false
}
